'''Ascwulf''' (or '''Æscwulf ''') was a medieval [[Bishop of Dunwich (ancient)|Bishop of Dunwich]]. He was bishop in the 8th century, but it is not known exactly when he was consecrated or his date of death.<ref name=HBOBC>{{cite book |author1=Fryde, E. B. |author2=Greenway, D. E. |author3=Porter, S. |author4=Roy, I. |title=Handbook of British Chronology |edition=3rd |publisher=Cambridge University Press |location=Cambridge |year=1986 |isbn=0-521-56350-X |page=216}}</ref>

